Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Google Web APIs for webometric studies, which involves analyzing and measuring various aspects of the web. This aligns with several sub-categories in computer science, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
